  "title": "Talkers Wanted — Sales Edition",
  "description": "<p><strong>✈️ We’re Expanding — and We Want You!</strong></p>\n<p>New projects, new countries, new opportunities. We’re growing fast and looking for new faces to join our team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>💼 Position: Sales &amp; Marketing Rep</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Type: Full-Time | No Experience Needed</p>\n<p>Looking for a fresh start or new challenge? We’ll train you from scratch — all you need is a great attitude and willingness to learn!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🌟 What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Represent well-known brands</li>\n  <li>Talk to customers &amp; share product info</li>\n  <li>Support marketing events &amp; campaigns</li>\n  <li>Work with a fun and motivated team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>💪 What You’ll Bring:</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ Positive and outgoing attitude</p>\n<p>✔️ Good communication skills</p>\n<p>✔️ Eager to learn and grow</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🎁 What You’ll Get:</strong></p>\n<p>🎓 Training provided for all stages!</p>\n<p>📈 Career growth opportunities</p>\n<p>🌏 Travel exposure (Taiwan, Australia, Korea &amp; more!)</p>",
